"business" includes the following, whether carried on by
Section 1 person or 2 or more people together:
         (a)     a profession or trade;
         (b)     any other activity carried on for fee, gain or reward;
         (c)     the activity of employing 1 or more people who perform duties in
connection with another business;
         (d)     the carrying on of a trust (including a dormant trust);
         (e)     the activity of holding any money or property used in connection with
another business.
